{"tid":1375370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"從警廉衝突就睇到點解成立唔到獨立調查委員會同埋警黑合作","createTime":"2019-07-28T04:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T01:50:59.000Z","uid":281020,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"353ceedbf3f40bbc81dbc8b3bff137a4ea065554","tid":1375370,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:53:25.000Z","msg":"故事由1977年講起，當年香港既貪污問題嚴重，一直去到葛柏案被揭發，爆發「反貪污，捉葛柏」既示威之後，港督麥理浩就成立咗廉政公署，偵破咗葛柏案。但係成件事未完，廉政公署之後係咁查警察既貪污，嗰陣時啲黑警個個都驚自己奶野，又好撚憎廉政公署，結果就爆發咗警廉衝突。<br />\n<br />\n衝突期間，麥理浩就召開緊急會議，問駐港英軍可唔可以出手，填壓班黑警，結果駐港英軍強烈反對，最終麥理浩發出局部特赦令，特赦於1977年1月1日以前所有涉嫌貪污而未被檢控的公職人員，係冇革職架。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AD%A6%E5%BB%89%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25BB%2589%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp4PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=4d1b7539\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AD%A6%E5%BB%89%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81</a><br />\n<br />\n點解今時今日黑警可以玩到咁大，就係當年貪污都冇比人追究，去廉政公署曬馬政府就會屈服，今日員佐級街坊福利會咁大聲咁口響，就係知你政府唔敢做我，如果政府成立獨立調查委員會，佢地咪去政府總部圍林鄭囉，當年港督有駐港英軍都搞唔掂，今日林鄭乜都冇(解放軍係直轄於共產黨)，佢咪唔敢成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n同埋當年貪污嗰班黑警大多數都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇被革職</span></span>架，大家都知道Once you go black, you never go back，當年貪污嗰班黑警冇勾結黑社會咩?你覺得特赦咗之後班黑警同黑社會既關係會了斷咩?陋習一旦形成咗就好難改，同埋一代傳一代，你估班藍衫跟班白衫做野嗰陣，唔會學埋依啲陋習?所以今日警黑合作，係由1977年班黑警繼承落黎。<br />\n<br />\n全世界都覺得五大訴求之中，除咗撤回逃犯條例之外，成立獨立調查委員會係最容易做，依家我話比你聽成立獨立調查委員會係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最撚難做</span></span>，因為一做班黑警就會重演1977年咁去政府總部逼林鄭唔查，甚至<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要求特赦</span></span>班黑警。"},{"pid":"ee67740662909597aff082b6c4c9bddf8cc77ed7","tid":1375370,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:54:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4b86ea2a63d421d2c690c7e58483a603cbd3dff","tid":1375370,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:58:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5301a549585184113f9bd897f0d7ac8f79ee9c0f","tid":1375370,"uid":189430,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:59:58.000Z","msg":"咁岩啦唔使特赦<br />\n一齊死啦<br />\n一個告唔到就成隊一齊告<br />\n一個一個排住隊上庭<br />\n解散警隊然後再係其他紀律部隊抽調人手另組自衛隊<br />\n停哂班仆街唔俾出糧<br />\n除非審到佢地冇罪，否則都唔好諗做得返政府工<br />\n會用到好多錢但我相信香港人唔會放過呢班仆街<br />\n呢班拎住香港人血汗錢又打到香港人留血既人渣"},{"pid":"74fcdda95adef87fac086b2970567a210365c51a","tid":1375370,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:08:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"987794eb53448f00821905195035ced6f3b60323","tid":1375370,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:10:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d076b45901403c890daf5dcb3764e213cd47b601","tid":1375370,"uid":141793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:11:43.000Z","msg":"英軍點同解放軍比呀<br />\n百萬雄師呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d4efb41c6d4e3dee61a620e960151e3913a3e0","tid":1375370,"uid":214192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:20:43.000Z","msg":"就算爆發警方圍政總，林鄭都唔知敢唔敢向上面叫解放軍嚟鎮返班警<br />\n要知道出解放軍就意味住港共管治完全失效（連高壓都唔撚掂），而且解放軍會用啲咩方法鎮壓都唔知，分分鐘後患無窮，都仲未計班商家以後會點睇香港<br />\n佢依家點拆都唔撚掂，獨立調查就警察吵，唔獨立調查就越多市民吵<br />\n佢諗住繼續玩反對通知書，到遲啲香港人免疫左個反對之後佢就仆街<br />\n777已經喺條不生路度，我哋繼續堅持就會見到希望"},{"pid":"24a987b717290cfd89e41bfabe18bd5f39a7a04c","tid":1375370,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2017/03/%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2-%E5%BB%89%E6%94%BF%E5%85%AC%E7%BD%B2-%E8%AD%A6%E5%BB%89%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-20170331205129_1fcf_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2017%2F03%2F%25E5%25BB%2589%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E5%25BB%2589%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25BB%2589%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-20170331205129_1fcf_large.jpg&h=7bf24d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2019年，黑警在政府總部集會要求不調查<br />\nIn 2019,police gather at Central Government Offices to demand NO investigation.<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14bfe3150c67ef79b855d1e748293815e45ab3fc","tid":1375370,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:23:48.000Z","msg":"所以警犬同林鄭要一齊過"},{"pid":"03daa99d0965d8b4b127bebd4d74fab917652fa6","tid":1375370,"uid":53988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:29:45.000Z","msg":"黑警話問心無愧 但係又唔俾人查 可恥"},{"pid":"418e70bb515998ffd84d86553c0bb9bec3cb1bbe","tid":1375370,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/vdo/20170302/480pix/1488392876_1c16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2Fvdo%2F20170302%2F480pix%2F1488392876_1c16.jpg&h=728eabb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIn 2019,rampaging policemen attack HKSAR<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e811d4baeefcc2cab940e061d551eaa6b277b5","tid":1375370,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/blogger/2019/04/20190408_BLOG_COMMENT.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fblogger%2F2019%2F04%2F20190408_BLOG_COMMENT.jpeg&h=202cc4e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2019年警政衝突，一名在政總示威的黑警，企圖把當時的行政長官林鄭月娥（被扯bra帶者）拉出來 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54e6dd52382e6a2dfbaac24c46df33b64b53492","tid":1375370,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20131028/large/1382932324_2af2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20131028%2Flarge%2F1382932324_2af2.jpg&h=ab8afaa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在2019年的警政對峙事件中，政府人員堅守大門不讓警務人員進入<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef9a492814c552ea0175c4ad920cc927d0885a3d","tid":1375370,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/7a3b26/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_150225/20150225_1606b24e556d0e35737fzMhGHoUFA1JV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F7a3b26%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.discuss.com.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_150225%2F20150225_1606b24e556d0e35737fzMhGHoUFA1JV.jpg&h=61285f8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑警高呼自己係法治既最後一道線。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db33b2dababea16eb62721f3050091fea7bd8016","tid":1375370,"uid":41007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:00:58.000Z","msg":"由班黑警唔係政治中立，維護林鄭政權開始<br />\n<br />\n就知道林鄭根本唔會成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係班狗唔會再無的放矢與市民為敵<br />\n<br />\n佢哋係condom仔嚟㗎咋，俾人利用都唔知<br />\n<br />\n就算今日冇獨立調查委員會，我相信香港人一定會抗爭到有為止<br />\n<br />\n日後成立之時，睇下班condom仔點撚樣"},{"pid":"d91838a0b5abe5ef6f0699e845fdbf95d81dfccf","tid":1375370,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:14:22.000Z","msg":"大家要諗下，當我地成功之後要清算condom仔，我地係冇可能一下革30000人職，正如當年港督都只可以特赦而冇革職，大家都知班condom仔視兩萬三萬人工如命，佢地被革職之後，得毅進文憑又搵唔到工做，一班冇野做屎忽痕、懷恨在心、有訓練過既社會渣滓會做啲咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee8e85b0e5e6c24cce533bb5e28f4caba136125","tid":1375370,"uid":36845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:53:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港有６９７萬人</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d82e8ebd9f57daedb4d312270e3c6814b63528b7","tid":1375370,"uid":109032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d91838a0b5abe5ef6f0699e845fdbf95d81dfccf","tid":1375370,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:14:22.000Z","msg":"大家要諗下，當我地成功之後要清算condom仔，我地係冇可能一下革30000人職，正如當年港督都只可以特赦而冇革職，大家都知班condom仔視兩萬三萬人工如命，佢地被革職之後，得毅進文憑又搵唔到工做，一班冇野做屎忽痕、懷恨在心、有訓練過既社會渣滓會做啲咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:56:47.000Z","msg":"殺哂佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39ce7217f528f5a5692b7c75ae4bfb2e4a2f4b0","tid":1375370,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:50:59.000Z","msg":"推"}]}